          "Valentin/a Ulyanenko",
          "Your pack's ductus.   A bit fanatical about hunting down elders, researching clues about their whereabouts, and dealing with them.  You think they're a bit over the top but you're grateful that they saved"
        ],
        [
          "Martin/Maria Fontana",
          "You know this much - you're not supposed to talk about the circumstances surrounding their arrival with the pack  That was before your time, so you're happy to keep mum.   You wonder if they're really committed to the Cause as much as the rest of you, or if they're in it for themselves, and the chance to gain more power from the blood and souls of Elders you might find."
        ],
        [
          "Alexandru/dra Balcescu",
          "Of your packmates, the one you are closest to.   They've been trying to help you work through your need to cling to your humanity and get you on another Path.   It's a long process, and you're not sure yet about this whole thing, but you're also sure you don't want to end up like your sire."
        ],
        [
